original_title: Subway To Sally: Live in Wacken 2015
overview: SUBWAY TO SALLY are a phenomenon. Founded in 1992, the Potsdam Septet quickly gained a fan base through countless live performances and strong albums.  Today the seven musicians inspire thousands of fans across the German-speaking world. The band's trademark is rock and metal music, enriched with medieval melodies that give them their own charm.
